properties.name: Dickinson County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Summit Carbon Solutions sued landowners for access to survey private land. Summit voluntarily dismissed the case on 6/14/23.
properties.Litigation1: Title: SUMMIT CARBON SOLUTIONS LLC V DANIEL L WAHL FAMILY TRUST; Case: 03301 CVCV031712 (DICKINSON)

properties.name: Hardin County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Summit Carbon Solutions sued landowner for access to survey private land. The Court dismissed the case on 7/3/23 after Summit moved to dismiss.
properties.Litigation1: Title: SUMMIT CARBON SOLUTIONS LLC V. TERESA A. THOMS; Case: 02421 EQCV101941 (HARDIN)
properties.LitigationDesc2: Summit Carbon Solutions sued landowner for access to survey private land. The Court ruled in Summit's favor and found the Iowa survey entry law constitutional.
properties.Litigation2: Title: SUMMIT CARBON SOLUTIONS V. KENT KASISCHKE; Case: 02421 CVCV101911 (HARDIN)

properties.name: Shelby County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Summit Carbon Solutions challenged Shelby County's pipeline ordinance. On July 10, 2023, the Court ruled in Summit's favor to stop enforcement of the ordinance.
properties.Litigation1: Couser et al v. Shelby County, Iowa et al., Docket No. 1:22-cv-00020 (S.D. Iowa Nov 15, 2022)

properties.name: Story County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Summit Carbon Solutions is challenging Story County's pipeline ordinance.
properties.Litigation1: Couser et al v. Story County, Iowa et al, Docket No. 4:22-cv-00383 (S.D. Iowa Nov 14, 2022)
properties.LitigationDesc2: Navigator Heartland is challenging Story County's pipeline ordinance in federal court. Story County has filed two Motions to Dismiss.
properties.Litigation2: Navigator Heartland Greenway, LLC v. Story County, Iowa et al, Docket No. 4:23-cv-00013 (S.D. Iowa Jan 11, 2023)
properties.LitigationDesc3: Navigator Heartland is challenging Story County's pipeline ordinance in state court.
properties.Litigation3:
NAVIGATOR HEARTLAND GREENWAY LLC v.
STORY COUNTY, IOWA and STORY COUNTY BOARD OF SUPERVISORS,CASE NO. 4:23-cv-272 (S.D. Iowa July 28, 2023)

properties.name: Emmet County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Summit Carbon Solutions is suing Emmet County to challenge the legality of its pipeline ordinance. Trial is set for 5/20/24
properties.Litigation1: Couser et al v. Emmet County, Iowa et al, Docket No. 3:23-cv-03007 (N.D. Iowa Mar 28, 2023)
properties.LitigationDesc2: Summit Carbon Solutions sued landowners for access to survey private land. Summit voluntarily dismissed the case on 5/19/23.
properties.Litigation2: Title: SUMMIT CARBON SOLUTIONS V. VALEN, DENNIS & MATTHEW; Case: 03321 EQCV022231 (EMMET)
properties.LitigationDesc3: Navigator Heartland is suing Emmet County to challenge the legality of its pipeline ordinance. The case is moving forward on Navigator's claims that the ordinance is preempted by state and federal law and that it is invalid and unenforceable.
properties.Litigation3: Navigator Heartland Greenway LLC v. Emmet County, Iowa et al, Docket No. 3:23-cv-03013 (N.D. Iowa Apr 12, 2023)

properties.name: Woodbury County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Navigator Heartland sued landowners for access to survey private land. The Court held that Navigator did not provide sufficient notice to gain access to landowner's property. The Court found the land survey law constitutional.
properties.Litigation1: Title: NAVIGATOR HEARTLAND GREENWAY LLC V. HULSE, WILLIAM & VICKI; Case: 03971 EQCV204557 (WOODBURY)

properties.name: Clay County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Navigator Heartland sued landowner for access to survey private land. The Court ruled that Iowa's land surveys law is unconstitutional.
properties.Litigation1: Title: NAVIGATOR HEARTLAND GREENWAY, LLC V. MARTIN KOENIG; Case: 03211 EQCV034863 (CLAY)

properties.name: Bremer County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Navigator Heartland is suing Bremer County to challenge the legality of its pipeline ordinance. The case is moving forward on Navigator's claims that the ordinance is preempted by state and federal law and that it is invalid and unenforceable.
properties.Litigation1: Navigator Heartland Greenway LLC v. Bremer County, Iowa et al, Docket No. 6:23-cv-02030 (N.D. Iowa Apr 12, 2023)

properties.name: Polk County, IA
properties.LitigationDesc1: Summit Carbon Solutions is seeking an injunction to prevent the IUB from releasing Summit's pipeline mailing list. The District Court ruled in favor of the IUB. Summit appealed to the Iowa Supreme Court.
properties.Litigation1: Title: SUMMIT CARBON SOLUTIONS LLC V. IOWA UTILITIES BOARD; Case: 05771 CVCV062900 (POLK), Iowa SCT No. 22-1444
properties.LitigationDesc2: Navigator Heartland Greenway is seeking an injunction to prevent the IUB from releasing Navigator's pipeline mailing list. This case is stayed pending the outcome of the Summit case.
properties.Litigation2: Title: NAVIGATOR HEARTLAND GREENWAY LLC V. IOWA UTILITIES BOARD; Case: 05771 EQCE088024 (POLK)
properties.LitigationDesc3: Wolf Carbon Solutions is seeking an injunction to prevent the IUB from releasing Wolf's pipeline mailing list. Case is stayed pending the outcome of the Summit case.
properties.Litigation3: Title: WOLF CARBON SOLUTIONS V. IOWA UTILITIES BOARD; Case: 05771 EQCE088016 (POLK)
properties.LitigationDesc4: Wolf Carbon Solutions is seeking an injunction to prevent the IUB from releasing Wolf's pipeline mailing list #2. Case is stayed pending the outcome of the Summit case.
properties.Litigation4: Title: WOLF CARBON SOLUTIONS US V. IOWA UTILITIES BOARD; Case: 05771 EQCE088409 (POLK)
